Package oogasalad.editor.view

Class PropertiesTabComponentFactory

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.view.PropertiesTabComponentFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
EditorViewListener
public class PropertiesTabComponentFactory extends Object implements EditorViewListener
Builds the "Properties" tab UI, displaying Identity invalid input: '&' Hitbox data, etc. Implements EditorViewListener to update whenever the selected object changes.

      private TextField createHitboxTextField(String promptText, BiConsumer<UUID,Integer> setter)
      Factory method to create a TextField for a numeric hitbox property (X, Y, Width, Height). Attaches a listener that parses the input as an integer and updates the model via the setter.
      Parameters:
      promptText - The prompt text for the TextField.
      setter - A BiConsumer accepting the UUID and the parsed integer value to update the model.
      Returns:
      The configured TextField.

      private void refreshFields()
      Refreshes all editable fields in the UI by fetching the latest data for the selected object. If no object is selected, clears all fields. Runs on the JavaFX application thread.
